Pork Prices Weighs 3% in China’s Inflation: Statistics Bureau

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-09-21T02:14:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-21/pork-prices-weighs-3-in-china-s-inflation-statistics-bureau.html
Pork prices account for about 3
percent of overall weighting of  China ’s consumer price index,
Pang Xiaolin, head of the National Bureau of Statistics’s urban
department, said yesterday, according to a statement on the
bureau’s website.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
